The global train lighting market is projected to experience substantial growth during the forecast period of 2021 to 2029. One of the key factors contributing to this growth is the increasing focus on enhancing safety and security measures in the railway industry. The adoption of advanced lighting technologies such as LED lighting is gaining traction as it offers energy efficiency, durability, and better illumination. LED lighting segment is expected to witness significant growth owing to its long operational life and low maintenance requirements. Furthermore, the rising demand for passenger trains and high-speed trains is propelling the growth of the train lighting market.

